What pages are linked?

Front Home Page:

1. Contacts List
   1a. When clicked on this - will show a list of contacts, there is a view link
   1b. When you click on the VIEW LINK - this takes you to a page where you can view the person's address.

2. Add New Contacts
   2a. When clicked on on this - form will appear with inputs and a create button
   2b. When the create button is clicked, this form will get SUBMITTED to the "contacts list"

   The purpose is that when you click on the SUBMIT button, the information entered from the form should appear in the contacts list.
